OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777568753
OL,3,CNew appeal for information over 1975
OL,4,Cdeath of bus inspector
OL,6,FA new appeal for information has been
OL,7,Fmade about the shooting of a bus
OL,8,Finspector in Belfast more than half a
OL,9,Fcentury ago.
OL,11,FThe Independent Commission for
OL,12,FReconciliation and Information
OL,13,FRecovery (ICRIR), is investigating the
OL,14,Fdeath of Alex Millar at work in May
OL,15,F1975.
OL,17,FMr Millar was a 54-year-old Citybus
OL,18,Finspector and father of four. No one
OL,19,Fever claimed the killing.
OL,21,FHe was a captain in the UDA.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777568753
OL,3,CNew appeal for information over 1975
OL,4,Cdeath of bus inspector
OL,6,FIn a statement, the ICRIR said: "The
OL,7,FCommission understands Alex Millar was
OL,8,Fa member of the UDA at the time of his
OL,9,Fdeath in 1975.
OL,11,F"He was also a war veteran, a husband
OL,12,Fand a father-of-four. Every death
OL,13,Fassociated with the Troubles/Conflict
OL,14,Fis a tragedy. Every family who lost a
OL,15,Floved one experienced trauma and each
OL,16,Fdeserves to have their questions
OL,17,Fanswered.
OL,26,@nD@aOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777568753
OL,3,CNew appeal for information over 1975
OL,4,Cdeath of bus inspector
OL,6,F"We have a statutory duty to
OL,7,Finvestigate any deaths or serious
OL,8,Finjuries related to the Troubles/
OL,9,FConflict, if a request is made under
OL,10,Fthe Legacy Act 2023."
OL,12,FThe statement added: "Today's appeal
OL,13,Ffor information is central to
OL,14,Funcovering the truth for Alex Millar's
OL,15,Ffamily who have waited more than five
OL,16,Fdecades to learn what happened that
OL,17,Fday."
OL,26,@yD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777568753
OL,3,CNew appeal for information over 1975
OL,4,Cdeath of bus inspector
OL,6,FICRIR assistant commissioner, Amanda
OL,7,FLogan said Mr Millar's family had
OL,8,Frequested an investigation "to find
OL,9,Fthe truth about his death".
OL,11,FShe said: "Alex was killed more 50
OL,12,Fyears ago and for all this time the
OL,13,FMillar family have carried the pain of
OL,14,Ftheir loss.
OL,16,F"In many of our investigations the
OL,17,Fsmallest details have proven vitally
OL,18,Fimportant.
OL,26,@pD@\OUqD@ZO]sD@KOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777568753
OL,3,CNew appeal for information over 1975
OL,4,Cdeath of bus inspector
OL,6,F"There may be people who witnessed the
OL,7,Fevents of that day and have lived with
OL,8,Ftheir memories for over half a century.
OL,10,F"If you saw or heard anything that
OL,11,Frelates to Alex's death, I encourage
OL,12,Fyou to come forward to the commission
OL,13,Fand share what you know."
OL,15,FAt approximately 2.40pm on Friday May
OL,16,F2 1975, Mr Millar was working in the
OL,17,FTimekeepers' office at the former
OL,18,FArdoyne Citybus depot at the junction
OL,19,Fof Cranbrook Avenue and Ardoyne Road.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUuD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777568753
OL,3,CNew appeal for information over 1975
OL,4,Cdeath of bus inspector
OL,6,FTwo gunmen entered the bus depot and
OL,7,Fshot him several times. After the
OL,8,Fattack, the gunmen were seen entering
OL,9,Fa waiting blue vehicle on Cranbrook
OL,10,FAvenue.
OL,12,FMr Millar was critically injured and
OL,13,Flater died at the Royal Victoria
OL,14,FHospital.
OL,16,FOn the same evening an 18-year-old man
OL,17,Fwas shot at Alliance Avenue and was
OL,18,Fseriously injured but survived.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777568753
OL,3,CNew appeal for information over 1975
OL,4,Cdeath of bus inspector
OL,6,FThe ICRIR said this is believed to be
OL,7,Flinked to the shooting of Mr Millar
OL,8,Fearlier that day.
OL,10,FThe Commission is also interested in
OL,11,Fthe movements of a yellow Ford Cortina
OL,12,Fin Tyndale Grove in the weeks leading
OL,13,Fup to the incident.
OL,15,FMs Logan said the Millar family, along
OL,16,Fwith many others the ICRIR is working
OL,17,Fwith, deserve answers.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
