FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777568753
OL,3,CNew appeal for information over 1975
OL,4,Cdeath of bus inspector
OL,6,FShe said: "In many cases, families who
OL,7,Flost loved ones during the Troubles/
OL,8,FConflict are still waiting for the
OL,9,Ftruth.
OL,11,F"The Commission's job is to correct
OL,12,Fthat and this appeal for information
OL,13,Fis critical to providing answers for
OL,14,FAlex's family."
OL,16,FThe witness appeal will involve
OL,17,Fdistributing posters and an organised
OL,18,Fleaflet drop in the areas relating to
OL,19,Fthe investigation.
OL,26,@nD@KOUsD@AOUvD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
