OL,3,CNew appeal for information over 1975
OL,4,Cdeath of bus inspector
OL,6,FThe ICRIR was established by the
OL,7,Fprevious government's Legacy Act to
OL,8,Finvestigate outstanding Troubles
OL,9,Fdeaths.
OL,11,FThe Labour Government's new Legacy
OL,12,FBill, agreed as part of a joint
OL,13,Fframework with the Irish Government,
OL,14,Fwill put in place a reformed Legacy
OL,15,FCommission with enhanced powers.
OL,17,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,18,FITVX
OL,20,FSign up for our free weekly newsletter
OL,21,Fhere.
